TENANT_TYPE	COMPATIBILITY_MODE	STATUS	IN_RECYCLEBIN	LOCKED	TENANT_ROLE	SWITCHOVER_STATUS	LOG_MODE	SYNC_SCN	REPLAYABLE_SCN	READABLE_SCN	RECOVERY_UNTIL_SCN	UNIT_NUM	RESTORE_DATA_MODE
